{"tid":557131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「求救」我整唔左啊媽既耳環！","createTime":"2018-02-11T05:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T03:59:05.000Z","uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee7daf78e3da3d3757e7fcb82804862e7c25e94","tid":557131,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"啱啱去左轉朋友屋企<br />\n返到屋企摸一摸隻右耳發現唔見左<br />\n搵左成個屋企 都冇<br />\n好可能係街到唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有聽日起身睇下朋友會唔會見到係屋企<br />\n無論如何都諗住等天光之後出街搵多次<br />\n再去轉警署<br />\n係鑽石耳環黎，我唔知價錢係幾多<br />\n對耳環對我係好緊要，我對呢啲好少研究<br />\n有冇識睇既巴絲可以話我知呢款可以邊到買到<br />\n我真係唔想令到媽咪唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我依家得返一隻，其實啲珠寶行有冇得單買一邊？<br />\n大家入黎鬧我不孝點都好，我都會多謝大家幫我推<br />\n因為對耳環對我黎講真係好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/131656_459480a79b2dff9f7077b78412a066be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F131656_459480a79b2dff9f7077b78412a066be.png&h=f746bd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/131703_88aaeda9d11fbe949b8e62c395a40391.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F131703_88aaeda9d11fbe949b8e62c395a40391.png&h=bec472a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d678e2f29c23d0fab46d0a2794bfba44619da8f","tid":557131,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2202be62b087649e76dfbd5c98024fe2c753d1c7","tid":557131,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faef21c75d885007566cc7fb954280c8cbee62db","tid":557131,"uid":81218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"拎去mabelle嗰d睇下有冇同款買番比佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b75608ffe0fc4fbb52888d856f031d21330eae","tid":557131,"uid":4459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:24:22.000Z","msg":"好多珠寶行都可以訂造<br />\n你拎手上個隻叫佢跟住造多隻就得<br />\n搵d樓上/細舖食水無咁深<br />\n我諗幾千走唔甩"},{"pid":"a4cc4198b52788ce9109a4ce49b780030bc95433","tid":557131,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"faef21c75d885007566cc7fb954280c8cbee62db","tid":557131,"uid":81218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"拎去mabelle嗰d睇下有冇同款買番比佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然好白痴，但佢地係咪冇得單邊買？ 我仲係學生 冇咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3745ca551a55a5eecef486b87c0ba82385b40b","tid":557131,"uid":20750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"揾業餘工藝師幫手啦"},{"pid":"2216b74d255d3d293c4a96db1492428dc87756b7","tid":557131,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33b75608ffe0fc4fbb52888d856f031d21330eae","tid":557131,"uid":4459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:24:22.000Z","msg":"好多珠寶行都可以訂造<br />\n你拎手上個隻叫佢跟住造多隻就得<br />\n搵d樓上/細舖食水無咁深<br />\n我諗幾千走唔甩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:29:29.0